Package: rajiveplus
Title: RAJIVE+
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(given = "Mikhael",
           family = "Manurung",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "m.d.manuurng@lumc.nl"))
Description: Blazing fast re-implementation of the RAJIVE algorithm for joint and individual variation explained in multi-view data. This package provides a user-friendly interface to perform RAJIVE analysis, along with tools for visualization and interpretation of results.
